JOHANNESBURG - The Gauteng Education Department's online application system for 2018 admissions will go live from 8am Tuesday morning.* Click here to apply online.The registration period for grades one and eight will close on the 2 June.Gauteng Education MEC Panyaza Lesufi assured parents that technical glitches experienced last year have been fixed.READ: Still 40,000 pupils not placed before schools openLast year the system crashed on the first day, and frustrated parents complained about the system placing pupils in schools far from home.Lesufi says the process will be smoother this year, and has urged parents to apply early.eNCA